INSTALLATION PROCEDURE:

Installation assumes a system running Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6.x in
enforced mode with the dhcp package installed.


mkdir -p /cdg/adhoc/
cd /cdg/adhoc/
wget --no-check-certificate https://utveckling.its.chalmers.se/sites/\
utveckling.its.chalmers.se/files/adhoc-connect-x.y.z.tar
tar -xf adhoc-connect-x.y.z.tar
ln -s adhoc-connect-x.y.z adhoc-connect
restorecon -FR /cdg
rm adhoc-connect-x.y.z.tar

cd /etc/cron.d
ln -s /cdg/adhoc/adhoc-connect/etc/cron.d/adhoc-connect .
restorecon -F adhoc-connect 


---------------------------------------------------------------------------

UPGRADE PROCEDURE:

cd /cdg/adhoc/
wget --no-check-certificate https://utveckling.its.chalmers.se/sites/\
utveckling.its.chalmers.se/files/adhoc-connect-v.w.u.tar
tar -xf adhoc-connect-v.w.u.tar
restorecon -RF adhoc-connect-v.w.u

rm adhoc-connect
ln -s adhoc-connect-v.w.u adhoc-connect
restorecon -F adhoc-connect

rm adhoc-connect-v.w.u.tar
rm -rf adhoc-connect-x.y.z              (eventually)